full_text: Screened by NARA, 8/14/2023 B220326/32 DA SILVA ABEL TOLENTINO B - 220326 X-ray dated 7/10/91 P.A.VIEW OF THE CHEST: Pulmonary calcification noted in the right apex and left base.
